In the 19th century, many Russians tried hard to learn French. Not everyone succeeded. A purely historical coincidence - in that century we piled on the French. In the 20th century, many Russians stubbornly tried to learn German, while cursing even more. Another strange coincidence - in that century we piled on the Germans. In the 21st century, many Russians tried to learn to speak Ukrainian. Yes, and with English somehow did not work out ...